!! Font Family      | XTerm*faceSize | Alacritty*font.size (*)
!! ---------------- | -------------- | -------------------
!! Inconsolata      | 24             | 23.0
!! Source Code Pro  | 24             | 23.0
!! Hack             |                |
!! Droid Sans Mono  |                |
!!
!! (*): Alacritty*font.size seems to depend on video card and driver.
!!      On GTX 1050 Ti with nvidia driver, Alacritty*font.size=23.0
!!      is equivalent to Xterm*faceSize=24.

#define myFont      Inconsolata
#define myFontSize  24

!! Global Dark Background
*foreground:   white
*background:   black
*cursorColor:  white

!! NOTE: ``xrdb`` always starts relative to ``$HOME``, do not add "$HOME" or "~/"
#include ".Xresources.d/urxvt"
#include ".Xresources.d/xterm"
